  "detailed_description": "Your glorious regime is under attack!<br><br>Will you sit idly and eat burgers while the foreign invasion destroys your legacy? Or will you take the matter into your own hands, and deal with the invaders yourself?<br><br>Dear Leader is an Action Run and Gun game, where you control Kim Jong Un, Pulgosauri the communist kaiju monster, and the Supreme Leader's secondary form.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 6 Levels<br><br></li><li> 6 Different weapons<br><br></li><li> 3 Playable Characters<br><br></li><li> 2 Difficulty Levels, Easy and Normal<br><br></li><li> Partial Gamepad Support<br><br></li><li> 6 Languages.</li></ul>",
